tyle="width: 1200px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3817732" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/09-Blur-To-The-End-credit-UP-THE-GAME-BLUR@1200x900.jpg" alt="《Blur：To The End》剧照，摄影：UP THE GAME/BLUR" width="1200" height="900" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/09-Blur-To-The-End-credit-UP-THE-GAME-BLUR@1200x900.jpg 1200w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/09-Blur-To-The-End-credit-UP-THE-GAME-BLUR@1200x900-400x300.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/09-Blur-To-The-End-credit-UP-THE-GAME-BLUR@1200x900-800x600.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/09-Blur-To-The-End-credit-UP-THE-GAME-BLUR@1200x900-696x522.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/09-Blur-To-The-End-credit-UP-THE-GAME-BLUR@1200x900-1068x801.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3817732" class="wp-caption-text">图片来源：UP THE GAME/BLUR</figcaption></figure><p>当莫伊尔斯问他是否已经拿到门票时，詹姆斯回应了他之前的评论，说：“我不确定我是否会去。看，他们一直等到我们把所有垃圾都扔掉，这是非常有礼貌的。”</p><p>莫伊尔斯随后问詹姆斯是否认为 Blur 最近的重聚激发了<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/liam-gallagher">利亚姆</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/noel-gallagher">诺尔·加拉格尔的</a>复合，他回答道：“好吧，只是我总是读到有关以离婚告终的婚姻的可怕统计数据。以它结尾的乐队的统计数据显示，每个人都互相憎恨——很难想象有哪个乐队不会这样做。”</p><p>他接着说：“他们也是兄弟，你知道吗？我真的很高兴，也真的不会去。”</p><p>詹姆斯的乐队成员<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/graham-coxon">格雷厄姆·考克森 (Graham Coxon)</a>也对绿洲十月份的回归发表了评论，称这次巡演<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/blurs-graham-coxon-weighs-in-on-oasis-reunion-its-good-for-fans-3802154">“对他们有好处，对歌迷也有好处”</a> 。而且， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/blurs-damon-albarn-says-hed-put-money-on-an-oasis-reunion-3445677">达蒙·阿尔本 (Damon Albarn) 在 2023 年“押注”了绿洲重聚的机会</a>。 </p><figure id="attachment_3809656" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3809656" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3809656" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Liam-and-Noel-Gallagher-perform-as-Oasis.-CREDIT_-Dave-Hogan_Getty-Images.jpg" alt="" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Liam-and-Noel-Gallagher-perform-as-Oasis.-CREDIT_-Dave-Hogan_Getty-Images.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Liam-and-Noel-Gallagher-perform-as-Oasis.-CREDIT_-Dave-Hogan_Getty-Images-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Liam-and-Noel-Gallagher-perform-as-Oasis.-CREDIT_-Dave-Hogan_Getty-Images-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Liam-and-Noel-Gallagher-perform-as-Oasis.-CREDIT_-Dave-Hogan_Getty-Images-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Liam-and-Noel-Gallagher-perform-as-Oasis.-CREDIT_-Dave-Hogan_Getty-Images-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Liam-and-Noel-Gallagher-perform-as-Oasis.-CREDIT_-Dave-Hogan_Getty-Images-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3809656" class="wp-caption-text">利亚姆·加拉格尔和诺尔·加拉格尔饰演绿洲。图片来源：戴夫·霍根/盖蒂图片社</figcaption></figure><p>两个乐队在 20 世纪 90 年代英伦流行音乐鼎盛时期展开了一场传奇般的竞争。 9月，据透露， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/blur-vs-oasis-battle-to-be-retold-in-new-west-end-play-3791869">一部以紧张动荡时期为背景的西区戏剧将于明年首演</a>。</p><p>继 2025 年 7 月<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/oasis-reunion-tour-uk-ireland-stadium-2025-liam-noel-gallagher-tickets-3787539">在英国和爱尔兰进行一系列大型演出</a>后，Oasis <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/oasis-add-extra-dates-to-north-american-2025-reunion-tour-due-to-phenomenal-demand-3799159">将前往北美</a>，然后于 9 月底返回<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/oasis-wembley-stadium-extra-reunion-dates-tickets-invite-only-no-surge-pricing-3790552">伦敦温布利体育场进行两场额外演出</a>，然后<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/oasis-add-more-dates-to-australia-2025-reunion-tour-3801693">于 10 月前往澳大利亚</a>。</p><div class="td-a-ad id_inline_ad2 id_ad_content-horiz-center"><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/oasis-announce-south-korean-and-japan-dates-for-their-2025-reunion-tour-3814881">他们还将于 2025 年 10 月 21 日在韩国高阳体育场进行演出</a>，随后于 10 月 25 日和 26 日在日本东京巨蛋进行两场演出。</p><p>在得知他们将回归后， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/oasis-respond-to-glastonbury-2025-rumours-and-the-chances-of-other-festivals-3788269">Oasis 排除了在 2025 年格拉斯顿伯里音乐节上进行头条表演的可能性</a>，并表示明年夏天他们不会出现在任何其他音乐节上。<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/could-oasis-return-to-knebworth-in-2026-3792709">利亚姆和诺埃尔也驳斥了 2026 年重返纳贝沃斯的传言</a>。</p><p>其他新闻方面，上个月， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/primal-screams-bobby-gillespie-says-he-doesnt-social-climb-like-blurs-alex-james-3810805">Primal Scream 乐队的鲍比·吉莱斯皮 (Bobby Gillespie) 在乐队最新专辑《Come Ahead》的一篇文章中猛烈抨击了詹姆斯</a>，指责詹姆斯“攀爬社交”。</p></div><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/blurs-alex-james-says-he-genuinely-wont-be-going-to-see-oasis-3818822">Blur 的 Alex James 表示他“真的不会”看到 Oasis</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
